schemas/advance-wars.schema.json`.\n  `npm test` y los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1375","metadata":{"content":"st` y los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1376","metadata":{"content":"t` y los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1377","metadata":{"content":"` y los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1378","metadata":{"content":"y los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1379","metadata":{"content":"y los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#138","metadata":{"content":"en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1380","metadata":{"content":"los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1381","metadata":{"content":"los gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1382","metadata":{"content":"os gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1383","metadata":{"content":"s gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1384","metadata":{"content":"gates sin-drift de CI vuelven a verde.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Docum