7","metadata":{"content":"regla del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1458","metadata":{"content":"regla del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1459","metadata":{"content":"egla del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#146","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1460","metadata":{"content":"gla del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1461","metadata":{"content":"la del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1462","metadata":{"content":"a del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1463","metadata":{"content":"del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1464","metadata":{"content":"del perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1465","metadata":{"content":"el perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1466","metadata":{"content":"l perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1467","metadata":{"content":"perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1468","metadata":{"content":"perfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1469","metadata":{"content":"erfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#147","metadata":{"content":"### Added — familias declarativas `grids` + agregado cross-colección en `refs` (SPEC §11, segunda y tercera etapa)\n- **Familia `grids` declarativa** en el core: `{ rule, emptyRule?, collection|singleton,\n  shape?: { singleton, rowsField?, colsField? }, legend?: { rule, tileTarget, palField?,\n  palMax? } }` — valida filas de mapa/escena de ancho uniforme (autoconsistente contra la\n  primera fila, o contra una forma fija externa como `platform.rows`/`.cols` vía `shape`) y\n  resuelve cada símbolo de `legend`/`fill` contra tiles+paleta, sin ejecutar código de perfil.\n- **4 perfiles migrados** (mismos rule-ids, cero cambio de comportamiento observable):\n  `adventure`/`dungeon` (`scene-rows`/`scene-dims`/`scene-legend-ref`, autoconsistente) y\n  `monster-rpg`/`tower-defense` (`map-dims`","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1470","metadata":{"content":"rfil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1471","metadata":{"content":"fil.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1472","metadata":{"content":"il.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1473","metadata":{"content":"l.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1474","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1475","metadata":{"content":"### Added — S2 deprecation policy + versionado (`H-2.4`, `H-3.5`, `API1`, `D2`, `H-3.3`)\n- Nivel `deprecated` en el linter (`game-lint-core.js`): una regla marcada\n  `rule.deprecated = {since, removedIn}` emite un hallazgo `level: \"deprecated\"` con\n  `since`/`removedIn` y msg accionable. **No es error** (no rompe el gate); la regla sigue\n  aplicando hasta `removedIn`.\n- Regla `version-migration` (reemplaza a `version-compatible`): `data.version` vs\n  `profile.specVersion` → **warn** si el GAME.md es anterior (consulta `MIGRATION.md`),\n  **error** si es posterior al tooling.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1476","metadata":{"content":"ION.md`),\n  **error** si es posterior al tooling. El linter migra, no rechaza.\n- `MIGRATION.md`: guía de migración entre versiones (modelo semver, entradas por versión,\n  receta de renombrado `MOVES` → `ACTIONS` con script `sed`/`jq`, checklist).\n- `test/lifecycle.js`: verifica ciclo de vida (MIGRATION.md receta, CONTRIBUTING breaking,\n  SPEC §7.1, manifest `migrations`/`deprecatedRules`). 13 chequeos.\n- `manifest.json`: campo `migrations: {supported, doc}` (versiones soportadas + path a\n  `MIGRATION.md`) y `deprecatedRules` por perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1477","metadata":{"content":"` por perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1478","metadata":{"content":"por perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1479","metadata":{"content":"por perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#148","metadata":{"content":"nte) y\n  `monster-rpg`/`tower-defense` (`map-dims`/`map-legend-ref`, forma fija vía `platform`) —\n  la misma lógica estaba duplicada en JS en los 4.\n- **`refs[].target` acepta agregado cross-colección**: `arrayField` (+ `itemField`) además\n  de `collection` — el set válido se junta escaneando un array anidado en TODAS las\n  entradas de la colección, no solo `Object.keys`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1480","metadata":{"content":"or perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1481","metadata":{"content":"r perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1482","metadata":{"content":"perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1483","metadata":{"content":"perfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1484","metadata":{"content":"erfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1485","metadata":{"content":"rfil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1486","metadata":{"content":"fil (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1487","metadata":{"content":"il (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1488","metadata":{"content":"l (ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1489","metadata":{"content":"(ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#149","metadata":{"content":"entradas de la colección, no solo `Object.keys`. Cubre \"algún X entre N filas otorga el\n  valor Y\" como dato en vez de código a mano.\n- **`dungeon.warp-lock` migrado**: `warp.locked` exige un item que ALGÚN `pickup`, en\n  CUALQUIER escena, otorgue — antes un `Set` armado a mano en `ruleScenes`, ahora una\n  entrada declarativa de `refs`.\n- SPEC §6.1/§11 actualizado (grids + agregado cross-colección documentados; queda como\n  \"tercera etapa\" de reglas puras-de-datos — lo que sigue en `rules` es lógica genuinamente\n  no reducible a forma declarativa sin volverse un DSL). `test/profile-descriptor.js` cubre\n  las formas nuevas del descriptor (31 chequeos, de 28). Suite sin regresiones: mismas 136\n  reglas, 190 casos de conformidad, mutation audit 20/20.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1490","metadata":{"content":"(ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1491","metadata":{"content":"ciclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1492","metadata":{"content":"iclo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1493","metadata":{"content":"clo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1494","metadata":{"content":"lo de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1495","metadata":{"content":"o de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1496","metadata":{"content":"de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1497","metadata":{"content":"de vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1498","metadata":{"content":"e vida expuesto a agentes).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","tit