sperado vs actual) y feature request (caso de uso, solución).\n- `.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md`: plantilla de PR (changelog, testing, breaking changes).\n- `test/buildGame-content.js` ampliado a **9/9 perfiles** (tower-defense + 8) con\n  aserciones de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1528","metadata":{"content":"iones de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1529","metadata":{"content":"ones de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#153","metadata":{"content":"0 casos de conformidad, mutation audit 20/20.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1530","metadata":{"content":"nes de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1531","metadata":{"content":"es de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1532","metadata":{"content":"s de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1533","metadata":{"content":"de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1534","metadata":{"content":"de forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1535","metadata":{"content":"e forma por clave derivada (44 chequeos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1536","metadata":{"content":"forma por clave