0`; tabla de estructura con archivos de governance.\n- `game-lint.js`: `summary` añade `deprecated` (count); `--agent` da hint dedicado para\n  hallazgos `deprecated`.\n- `tools/rule-hints.js`: hint para `version-migration`.\n- `package.json` `test`: añade `test/lifecycle.js` y `test/perf-smoke.js`; CI `ci.yml`\n  añade `test/life","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1627","metadata":{"content":"st/perf-smoke.js`; CI `ci.yml`\n  añade `test/lifecycle.js` (perf-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1628","metadata":{"content":"(perf-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1629","metadata":{"content":"perf-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#163","metadata":{"content":"conformidad, mutation audit 20/20.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1630","metadata":{"content":"erf-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1631","metadata":{"content":"rf-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1632","metadata":{"content":"f-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1633","metadata":{"content":"-smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1634","metadata":{"content":"smoke corre solo en `npm test`, no en CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Document