tle":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1670","metadata":{"content":"n CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1671","metadata":{"content":"CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1672","metadata":{"content":"CI).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1673","metadata":{"content":"I).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1674","metadata":{"content":").","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1675","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1676","metadata":{"content":"### Breaking changes\n- **Política de versionado (no remoción de tokens).** Desde `1.0.0` los cambios breaking al core\n  y a los perfiles son bump **major** y **exigen** una deprecation previa (marcar\n  `deprecated: {since, removedIn}` + entrada `### Deprecated` en `CHANGELOG.md`). En `0.x` los\n  breaking eran bump **minor** (`0.1` → `0.2`). Esto cambia el contrato para *futuros* cambios;\n  no remueve ni renombra ningún token en este release. Ver [SPEC §7](./SPEC.md) y [§7.1](./SPEC.md).\n- **Regla `version-migration`** (reemplaza a `version-compatible`): un `GAME.md` con `version`\n  **mayor** que la soportada por el tooling ahora es **error** (antes era warn/ignorado). Los\n  `GAME.md` existentes en `0.1` siguen en 0 errores (warn → `MIGRATION.md`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1677","metadata":{"content":"1` siguen en 0 errores (warn → `MIGRATION.md`). Acción requerida\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1678","metadata":{"content":"uerida\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1679","metadata":{"content":"erida\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#168","metadata":{"content":"ormidad, mutation audit 20/20.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1680","metadata":{"content":"rida\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1681","metadata":{"content":"ida\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1682","metadata":{"content":"da\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1683","metadata":{"content":"a\n  solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1684","metadata":{"content":"solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1685","metadata":{"content":"solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1686","metadata":{"content":"solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1687","metadata":{"content":"solo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1688","metadata":{"content":"olo si declarabas una versión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md