},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1711","metadata":{"content":"ersión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1712","metadata":{"content":"rsión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1713","metadata":{"content":"sión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1714","metadata":{"content":"ión futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1715","metadata":{"content":"ón futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1716","metadata":{"content":"n futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1717","metadata":{"content":"futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1718","metadata":{"content":"futura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1719","metadata":{"content":"utura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#172","metadata":{"content":"dad, mutation audit 20/20.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1720","metadata":{"content":"tura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1721","metadata":{"content":"ura.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1722","metadata":{"content":"ra.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1723","metadata":{"content":"a.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1724","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1725","metadata":{"content":"### Caveats\n- **`version` del protocolo vs. release del paquete.** La *versión del protocolo* (`SPEC.md`\n  header y el campo `version` que declaran los `GAME.md`) sigue siendo `0.1`; el *release del\n  paquete* (`package.json`) reacha `1.0.0`. Son independientes: una futura edición del spec\n  moverá la versión del protocolo; hasta entonces, `0.1` sigue siendo la versión soportada\n  (`manifest.json` → `migrations.supported: [\"0.1\"]`).\n- **`render-png.js`** solo soporta el perfil `adventure` (lee `G.SCENE.tilemap`/`attrs`). Un\n  generado de otro perfil sale con exit `2` y mensaje accionable, no con un `TypeError` crudo.\n- **Sin dependencias.** Las herramientas son Node puro (>=18); no hay `npm install`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1726","metadata":{"content":"entas son Node puro (>=18); no hay `npm install`. En Windows,\n  `.gitattributes` (`* text=auto eol=lf`) mitiga el drift CRLF del generado.\n\n### Seguridad (heredada de la fase INMEDIATO, documentada en `0.1.0`)\n- S1: prototype pollution en el parser YAML (`__proto__`, `constructor`).\n- S2: path traversal + RCE vía perfil inválido (validación `/^[a-z0-9-]+$/`).\n- S3: `new Function()` en `render-png.js` → `require()` con path-check.\n- Estas correcciones se publicaron en `0.1.0` y se mantienen en `1.0.0`.\n\n## [0.1.0] — 2026-06-22 — fase CORTO","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1727","metadata":{"content":".0.0`.\n\n## [0.1.0] — 2026-06-22 — fase CORTO\n\n### Added\n- Core genérico sin dependencias: parser YAML, linter, compilador.\n- 8 perfiles cargables (monster-rpg, platformer, adventure, crafting, dungeon, papers-please, roguelike, voxel).\n- CI con gate sin-drift: manifest, schemas, ejemplos.\n- Demos jugables: roguelike, dungeon, adventure (+ voxel 3D viewer).\n- Bucle agente LLM: `--agent` mode con hints accionables.\n- `test/cli-errors.js`, `test/buildGame-content.js`, `test/build-standalone.js`.\n- `.gitattributes` (`* text=auto eol=lf`): mitiga drift CRLF en Windows.\n- `PLAN-MEDIANO.md`: roadmap post-CORTO.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1728","metadata":{"content":"indows.\n- `PLAN-MEDIANO.md`: roadmap post-CORTO.\n\n### Fixed\n- `game-export.js` / `build-standalone.js`: archivo inexistente ahora exit 2 con mensaje claro.\n- S1: Prototype pollution en parser YAML (`__proto__`, `constructor`).\n- S2: Path traversal + RCE vía profile inválido (validar `/^[a-z0-9-]+$/`).\n- S3: `new Function()` en `render-png.js` → `require()` con path-check.\n- M1: README referencia `game-build.js` inexistente (→ `game-build-core.js`).\n\n### Known Issues (resueltos en `1.0.0`)\n- Sin política de deprecation → resuelto en S2.\n- `tower-defense` listado como planned en SPEC §9 → implementado en S1.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1729","metadata":{"content":"como planned en SPEC §9 → implementado en S1.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#173","metadata":{"content":"ad, mutation audit 20/20.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1730","metadata":{"content":"omo planned en SPEC §9 → implementado en S1.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1731","metadata":{"content":"mo planned en SPEC §9 → implementado en S1.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1732","metadata":{"content":"o planned en SPEC §9 → implementado en S1.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#1733","metadata":{"content":"planne