G.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#24","metadata":{"content":"rotocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#240","metadata":{"content":"da pasada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#241","metadata":{"content":"a pasada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#242","metadata":{"content":"pasada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#243","metadata":{"content":"pasada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#244","metadata":{"content":"asada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#245","metadata":{"content":"sada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#246","metadata":{"content":"ada.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#247","metadata":{"content":"da.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#248","metadata":{"content":"a.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#249","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#25","metadata":{"content":"otocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#250","metadata":{"content":"**Guardado automático** de la\n  run en localStorage (`rgSave`/`rgLoad` puros y testeados; N = nueva partida; el\n  guardado se limpia al ganar o caer en permadeath) y **estadísticas de run** en los\n  overlays (salas, bajas, caídas, profundidad máxima).\n- **+17 chequeos en `npm test` y CI** (171 de lógica): solvencia por BFS, cerraduras\n  y llaves generadas, unlock que abre ambos lados, jefe que bloquea/daña/cae,\n  levelup con tope, permadeath → gameover, save/load ida y vuelta, y el **bot\n  explorador ONLINE que gana jugando** (rutea por el grafo conocido, toma salidas\n  inexploradas y derrota al jefe antes del cofre).\n- **Verificado en navegador en ambos motores**: el 2D con la lógica compartida\n  (puerta cerrada/llave con los textos del GAME.md) y game3d con guardado +\n  restaur","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#251","metadata":{"content":"tos del GAME.md) y game3d con guardado +\n  restauración tras recargar, nueva partida con N y victoria del explorador por\n  eventos de teclado reales — misma firma de run que el test de Node (6 salas,\n  1 baja, prof. 5): mismo mundo otra vez.\n- Nota: añadir tiradas al generador cambia los mundos respecto a v2.16.0 — la\n  paridad garantizada es entre motores, no con releases anteriores.\n\n## [2.16.0] — 2026-07-08\n\nRelease **aditivo** sobre `2.15.0` (bump minor, [SPEC §7.0](./SPEC.md)): el visor\n`advance-wars` completa el tablero — **los 14 perfiles del repo tienen runtime en\ngame3d**. Donde el perfil solo modela arte, el runtime no inventa gameplay: esa es la\ntesis del protocolo aplicada hasta el final. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#252","metadata":{"content":"final. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#253","metadata":{"content":"inal. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#254","metadata":{"content":"nal. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#255","metadata":{"content":"al. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#256","metadata":{"content":"l. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#257","metadata":{"content":". La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#258","metadata":{"content":"La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#259","metadata":{"content":"La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#26","metadata":{"content":"tocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#260","metadata":{"content":"a versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#261","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#262","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#263","metadata":{"content":"ersión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#264","metadata":{"content":"rsión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#265","metadata":{"content":"sión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title"