n  mulberry32, mismo hash de coordenadas, mismas reglas de puertas/escaleras mutuas y\n  cofre en la primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#35","metadata":{"content":"gue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#350","metadata":{"content":"en la primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#351","metadata":{"content":"en la primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#352","metadata":{"content":"n la primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#353","metadata":{"content":"la primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#354","metadata":{"content":"la primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#355","metadata":{"content":"a primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#356","metadata":{"content":"primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#357","metadata":{"content":"primera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#358","metadata":{"content":"rimera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#359","metadata":{"content":"imera sala a profundidad ≥ `maxDepth`.","okf_concept":"