t":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#484","metadata":{"content":"ue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#485","metadata":{"content":"e en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#486","metadata":{"content":"en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#487","metadata":{"content":"en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#488","metadata":{"content":"n `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#489","metadata":{"content":"`0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#49","metadata":{"content":"tos, y 4 razones concretas\n  de por qué importa. Publicada en GitHub Pages: https://mauricioperera.github.io/game-protocol/\n- **El listado de demos existente se preserva intacto en `demos.html`** (mismo contenido,\n  mismas rutas relativas), ahora linkeado desde el nav/footer de la nueva home.\n- **Soporte multi-idioma (ES/EN/PT) en ambas páginas**: selector en el nav, detección por\n  `navigator.language` (fallback ES) persistida en `localStorage` bajo la clave\n  compartida `gp-lang` — el idioma elegido se mantiene al navegar entre `index.html` y\n  `demos.html`. 71 claves traducidas en `index.html`, 24 en `demos.html`; el código real\n  de `GAME.md` (tokens del protocolo) no se toca, solo la prosa explicativa.\n- README actualizado con los links a la página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#490","metadata":{"content":"`0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#491","metadata":{"content":"0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#492","metadata":{"content":".1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#493","metadata":{"content":"1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#494","metadata":{"content":"`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#495","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#496","metadata":{"content":"### Added — runtime `platformer` en game3d\n- **Runtime `platformer`** (11º perfil jugable): el artefacto ya generado corre en\n  game3d sin tocar core ni datos — vista lateral 3D con cámara que sigue al jugador,\n  suelo coloreado por `tileset`, enemigos por hp, bandera en `goal.x`, parpadeo de\n  invulnerabilidad; ←/→ corre y Espacio/↑ salta (teclas mantenidas).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#497","metadata":{"content":"→ corre y Espacio/↑ salta (teclas mantenidas).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#498","metadata":{"content":"corre y Espacio/↑ salta (teclas mantenidas).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#499","metadata":{"content":"corre y Espacio/↑ salta (teclas mantenidas).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#5","metadata":{"content":"o. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#50","metadata":{"content":"lizado con los links a la página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#500","metadata":{"content":"orre