1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#589","metadata":{"content":"1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#59","metadata":{"content":"n los links a la página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#590","metadata":{"content":"`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#591","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#592","metadata":{"content":"### Added — runtime `tower-defense` en game3d\n- **Runtime `tower-defense`** (10º perfil jugable): el artefacto ya generado corre en\n  game3d sin tocar core ni datos — tablero 3D completo (rejilla 12×8, camino, torres\n  como cilindros por tipo, enemigos como esferas por blindaje), cursor con flechas,\n  construir con 1..N, vender con S (a `sellRatio`), oleadas con Espacio, overlays de\n  victoria/derrota. El runtime expone `step()` para pilotar ticks desde harnesses.\n- **Lógica pura en `game3d-logic.mjs`** (`tdPath`/`tdPos`/`tdInit`/`tdBuild`/`tdSell`/\n  `tdStartWave`/`tdTick`, +11 chequeos en `npm test` y CI): simulación por ticks **sin\n  azar** (spawns por count/gap, targeting al enemigo más avanzado en rango, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#593","metadata":{"content":"rango, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#594","metadata":{"content":"rango, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#595","metadata":{"content":"ango, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#596","metadata":{"content":"ngo, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#597","metadata":{"content":"go, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#598","metadata":{"content":"o, daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#599","metadata":{"content":", daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#6","metadata":{"content":". La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#60","metadata":{"content":"los links a la página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#600","metadata":{"content":"daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#601","metadata":{"content":"daño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#602","metadata":{"content":"año por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#603","metadata":{"content":"ño por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#604","metadata":{"content":"o por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#605","metadata":{"content":"por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#606","metadata":{"content":"por\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#607","metadata":{"content":"or\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#608","metadata":{"content":"r\n  `DMG_CHART[dmgType][armor]`). Partida **ganada y perdida en Node**: 4 rifles\n  centrales superan las 2 oleadas (15/15 abatidos, 0 fugas) y sin torres se pierde;\n  conservación verificada en cada tick (aparecidos = muertos + fugados + vivos);\n  venta a `floor(cost·sellRatio)`; construir sobre el camino o sin oro → `blocked`.\n- Semántica del motor documentada (SPEC §8): el ejemplo no declara `MAPS`, así que el\n  camino es una ruta en S fija sobre 12×8; 30 ticks ≈ 1 s (speed = celdas/s, rate =\n  disparos/s, gap en ticks); recompensa y luego interés al limpiar la oleada.\n- **Verificado jugando en navegador**: torres construidas con teclado real, intento\n  ilegal sobre el camino rechazado, 2 oleadas pilotando `step()` hasta el overlay de\n  victoria (oro final 186, vidas 20/20).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#609","metadata":{"content":"rlay de\n  victoria (oro final 186, vidas 20/20).\n\n## [2.11.0] — 2026-07-08\n\nRelease **aditivo** sobre `2.10.0` (bump minor, [SPEC §7.0](./SPEC.md)): el artefacto\n`papers-please` ya generado se vuelve jugable en game3d — sin tocar core ni datos, con\nla evaluación por RULES verificada contra las decisiones declaradas del ejemplo. La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#61","metadata":{"content":"los links a la página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#610","metadata":{"content":"emplo. La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#611","metadata":{"content":"mplo. La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#612","metadata":{"content":"plo. La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#613","metadata":{"content":"lo. La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#614","metadata":{"content":"o. La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#615","metadata":{"content":". La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#616","metadata":{"content":"La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#617","metadata":{"content":"La\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#618","metadata":{"content":"a\nversión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#619","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#62","metadata":{"content":"os links a la página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#620","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf