e":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#743","metadata":{"content":"en navegador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#744","metadata":{"content":"n navegador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#745","metadata":{"content":"navegador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#746","metadata":{"content":"navegador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#747","metadata":{"content":"avegador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#748","metadata":{"content":"vegador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#749","metadata":{"content":"egador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#75","metadata":{"content":"página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#750","metadata":{"content":"gador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#751","metadata":{"content":"ador.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#752","metadata":{"content":"dor.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#753","metadata":{"content":"or.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#754","metadata":{"content":"r.**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#755","metadata":{"content":".**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#756","metadata":{"content":"**","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#757","metadata":{"content":"*","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#758","metadata":{"content":"### Added — perfil `sudoku` (puro-datos) + Sudoku\n- Nacido de una interpretación errónea de «senku» (es el solitario de clavijas, no el\n  sudoku); el trabajo quedó completo y verificado, así que se conserva como perfil\n  propio con el juego renombrado a `examples/sudoku.GAME.md`.\n- **`profiles/sudoku.json`** (13º perfil, tercer puro-datos): puzzles como strings de\n  81 caracteres (`grid` con `.` + `solution`), `difficulty` por enum, `player.start`\n  por broken-ref y `balance` (lives/hints).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#759","metadata":{"content":"tart`\n  por broken-ref y `balance` (lives/hints). Límite documentado: longitud/patrón de los\n  strings y la consistencia grid↔solution **no caben en las familias declarativas** —\n  las valida `sudokuCheck` en la simulación de referencia y en `npm test` (segundo caso\n  concreto para SPEC §11: validadores de patrón/longitud de string).\n- **`examples/sudoku.GAME.md`** (+ generated): 3 puzzles **generados por script con\n  verificación de unicidad** (backtracking + conteo de soluciones; easy 40 / normal 32\n  / hard 27 pistas) — ni un dígito escrito a mano.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#76","metadata":{"content":"página y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#760","metadata":{"content":"hard 27 pistas) — ni un dígito escrito a mano. Lint 0/0 a la primera.\n- **Lógica pura en `game3d-logic.mjs`** (`sudokuCheck`/`sudokuInit`/`sudokuSet`/\n  `sudokuHint`, +14 chequeos en `npm test` y CI): los 3 puzzles reales validados\n  (consistencia + validez por filas/columnas/cajas), victoria rellenando la solución,\n  derrota al agotar vidas, pistas dadas inmutables, hint con descuento.\n- **Runtime `sudoku` en game3d** (7º perfil jugable): tablero DOM 9×9 sobre fondo 3D,\n  flechas + dígitos + H para pista, overlays de victoria/derrota. **Verificado jugando\n  en navegador**: pista inmutable, fallo que descuenta vida, hint, y tablero resuelto\n  hasta el overlay de victoria.\n- README: 128 → **133 reglas** (reconteo por script tras ambos perfiles).\n\n## [2.9.0] — 2026-07-08","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#761","metadata":{"content":"tras ambos perfiles).\n\n## [2.9.0] — 2026-07-08\n\nRelease **aditivo** sobre `2.8.1` (bump minor, [SPEC §7.0](./SPEC.md)): un género nuevo\nde punta a punta sin tocar el core — perfil puro-datos `shooter`, el juego Neon Swarm,\nsu simulación pura **ganada y perdida en Node dentro de `npm test`**, y su runtime en\ngame3d. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#762","metadata":{"content":"ame3d. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#763","metadata":{"content":"me3d. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#764","metadata":{"content":"e3d. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#765","metadata":{"content":"3d. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#766","metadata":{"content":"d. La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#767","metadata":{"content":". La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#768","metadata":{"content":"La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#769","metadata":{"content":"La versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#77","metadata":{"content":"ágina y a los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#770","metadata":{"content":"a versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#771","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#772","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#773","metadata":{"content":"ersión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#774","metadata":{"content":"rsión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#775","metadata":{"content":"sión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#776","metadata":{"content":"ión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#777","metadata":{"content":"ón del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#778","metadata":{"content":"n del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concep