t":"`0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#856","metadata":{"content":"0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#857","metadata":{"content":".1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#858","metadata":{"content":"1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#859","metadata":{"content":"`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#86","metadata":{"content":"los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#860","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#861","metadata":{"content":"### Added — mejoras del runtime game3d\n- **Runtime `quiz`**: el perfil puro-datos gana su primera demo jugable — rondas,\n  timer por pregunta (`seconds`), puntuación (`points` + `reward` por ronda), teclas\n  1-N para responder, overlay final con aciertos. Fondo 3D de cubos por categoría.\n  Verificado con partida perfecta scriptada: 5/5 aciertos y **450 pts exactos** (la\n  suma derivada de los datos).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#862","metadata":{"content":"pts exactos** (la\n  suma derivada de los datos). En el selector del player.\n- **Lógica pura extraída y testeada** (`examples/game3d-logic.mjs` +\n  `test/game3d-logic.js`, 25 chequeos en `npm test` y CI): fórmulas de combate\n  deterministas (daño con eficacia/varianza/nivel/slow, con `rnd` inyectado), captura\n  (la fórmula de `BALANCE`), XP/niveles/evoluciones, colisión de grid y visión de\n  entrenadores — el motor entra a la disciplina de verificación del repo. `game3d.js`\n  consume el módulo (sin THREE/DOM en la lógica).","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#863","metadata":{"content":"consume el módulo (sin THREE/DOM en la lógica). Cambio menor asumido: el daño del\n  rival ahora aplica el mismo factor de nivel simétrico que el del jugador.\n- **Tween de movimiento + orientación del sprite** en los runtimes tile y monster-rpg:\n  el estado sigue siendo instantáneo (lógica y tests intactos) y el sprite interpola\n  la posición; `face` voltea el billboard según la dirección horizontal.\n\n## [2.7.1] — 2026-07-07\n\nRelease **patch** sobre `2.7.0` ([SPEC §7.0](./SPEC.md)): refactor sin cambio de\ncontrato — una sola implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#864","metadata":{"content":"a sola implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#865","metadata":{"content":"sola implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#866","metadata":{"content":"sola implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#867","metadata":{"content":"ola implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#868","metadata":{"content":"la implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#869","metadata":{"content":"a implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#87","metadata":{"content":"los demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#870","metadata":{"content":"implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#871","metadata":{"content":"implementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#872","metadata":{"content":"mplementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#873","metadata":{"content":"plementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#874","metadata":{"content":"lementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#875","metadata":{"content":"ementación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#876","metadata":{"content":"mentación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#877","metadata":{"content":"entación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#878","metadata":{"content":"ntación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#879","metadata":{"content":"tación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#88","metadata":{"content":"os demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#880","metadata":{"content":"ación del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#881","metadata":{"content":"ción del motor monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELO