og"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#894","metadata":{"content":"r monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#895","metadata":{"content":"monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#896","metadata":{"content":"monster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#897","metadata":{"content":"onster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#898","metadata":{"content":"nster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#899","metadata":{"content":"ster-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#9","metadata":{"content":"a versión del protocolo sigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#90","metadata":{"content":"demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#900","metadata":{"content":"ter-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#901","metadata":{"content":"er-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#902","metadata":{"content":"r-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#903","metadata":{"content":"-rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#904","metadata":{"content":"rpg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#905","metadata":{"content":"pg 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#906","metadata":{"content":"g 3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#907","metadata":{"content":"3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#908","metadata":{"content":"3D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#909","metadata":{"content":"D.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#91","metadata":{"content":"demos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#910","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#911","metadata":{"content":"### Changed\n- **Runtime monster-rpg unificado**: `examples/kaiju-island-3d.html` ya no lleva su\n  copia inline del motor — redirige al player multi-perfil\n  (`game3d.html?game=kaiju-island.generated.js`), cuyo runtime monster-rpg es la\n  versión generalizada del mismo motor. Una sola implementación.\n- Retirado `examples/kaiju-island-3d-standalone.html`: contenía la copia duplicada, y\n  `build-standalone` no puede inlinar módulos ES (el motor unificado se importa como\n  módulo), así que no podía reconstruirse.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#912","metadata":{"content":"omo\n  módulo), así que no podía reconstruirse. El juego sigue disponible standalone-menos\n  vía `game3d.html` servido junto a `game3d.js`.\n- Diferencias menores asumidas al generalizar (documentadas): el terreno de respaldo\n  para áreas sin mapa es genérico (no la playa fija de shore) y no hay bonus específico\n  de STORM_BALL (el runtime no hardcodea nombres de items).\n\n## [2.7.0] — 2026-07-07\n\nRelease **aditivo** sobre `2.6.0` (bump minor, [SPEC §7.0](./SPEC.md)): el runtime\nmulti-perfil `game3d` — la respuesta práctica a \"¿motor universal?\": no existe por\ndiseño (el protocolo declara datos; la semántica de cada género es del motor, SPEC §8),\npero un player único con un módulo de runtime por perfil sí. La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#913","metadata":{"content":"l sí. La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#914","metadata":{"content":"sí. La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#915","metadata":{"content":"sí. La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#916","metadata":{"content":"í. La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#917","metadata":{"content":". La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#918","metadata":{"content":"La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#919","metadata":{"content":"La versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#92","metadata":{"content":"emos.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#920","metadata":{"content":"a versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#921","metadata":{"content":"versión del protocolo\nsigue en `0.1`.","okf_concept":"CHANGELOG.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"Changelog"}},{"id":"CHANGELOG.md#922