d","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#171","metadata":{"content":"e entra:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#172","metadata":{"content":"entra:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#173","metadata":{"content":"entra:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#174","metadata":{"content":"ntra:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#175","metadata":{"content":"tra:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#176","metadata":{"content":"ra:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#177","metadata":{"content":"a:","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#178","metadata":{"content":":","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#179","metadata":{"content":"- **Perfil `tower-defense`** — nuevo género con 8 claves de balance (`TOWERS`, `DMG_CHART`, `ENEMIES`, `ARMORS`, `WAVES`, `MAPS`, `ECONOMY`, `BALANCE`) + arte; demo jugable en `examples/tower-defense.html`. Lleva el total a **9 perfiles** cargables (ver [SPEC §6](./SPEC.md)).\n- **Deprecation policy** — nivel `deprecated` en el linter + regla `version-migration` (el linter *migra, no rechaza*) + `MIGRATION.md` con recetas de renombrado + `manifest.json` exponiendo `migrations`/`deprecatedRules`.","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#18","metadata":{"content":"íneas.\n\n---\n\n## Estructura del repo","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#180","metadata":{"content":".json` exponiendo `migrations`/`deprecatedRules`. Contrato completo en [SPEC §7.1](./SPEC.md).\n- **Performance + helpers compartidos** — `tools/profile-helpers.js` (una sola definición reusada por manifest/schema/perfiles); `lintGame` sobre 10K datos < 50ms (mediana ~3ms); edge cases del parser (clave duplicada, string sin cerrar, indentación con TAB, guard de profundidad).\n- **Governance** — `CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md`, `CODEOWNERS`, plantillas de issue/PR (`.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/`, `.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md`).\n- **buildGame 9/9** — `test/buildGame-content.js` cubre los 9 perfiles con aserciones de forma por clave derivada.\n- **Docs finales alineados** — SPEC/README/CONTRIBUTING/MIGRATION/CHANGELOG sincronizados a `v1.0.0`.\n\n### Fase MEDIANO completada ✅","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#181","metadata":{"content":"dos a `v1.0.0`.\n\n### Fase MEDIANO completada ✅\n\nLa fase MEDIANO del roadmap (sobre la base de CORTO) está verde cuando **todos**\nestos puntos pasan simultáneamente (ver [`PLAN-MEDIANO.md`](./PLAN-MEDIANO.md)):","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#182","metadata":{"content":"te (ver [`PLAN-MEDIANO.md`](./PLAN-MEDIANO.md)):","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#183","metadata":{"content":"e (ver [`PLAN-MEDIANO.md`](./PLAN-MEDIANO.md)):","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#184","metadata":{"content":"(ver [`PLAN-MEDIANO.md`](./PLAN-MEDIANO.md)):","okf_concept":"README.md","okf_type":"Documentation","title":"GAME Protocol — *Gameplay as Data*"}},{"id":"README.md#1